  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Subsequently, we then searched these proteins against the SIFT database 51 (as of December 2022) to filter out proteins lacking experimentally determined functional annotations.",
    "As a result, we obtained 6229 proteins of less than 1024 residues as an independent hold-out test set.",
    "We implemented the trained PhiGnet to assign function annotations to these recently released proteins, and the predictions are evaluated against the annotations in the SIFT database.",
    "To calculate evolutionary couplings, we collected an MSA for the target protein by searching its sequence against the UniClust30 database (up to February 2022) 52 using the hhblits tool 53 (version 3.3.0) with default parameters.",
    "Afterward, we performed trimming on each MSA using in-house scripts to eliminate sequences of low quality (for instance, sequences with over 80% gaps were removed)."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
